name.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Use media keys to control Yousee Music

short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Press Play/Stop/Next/Prev keys to control the playback of your current playlist

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Enables media keys to be used while listening to music on musik.yousee.dk

Version 1.6 fixes support of the latest layout changes on yousee musik.
